# App Profiling (AI diagnosis)

**Status:** v0.8.276. Off by default. **Not** workflow-only — full app trace.

## Enable

**프로그램 설정 → 진단** or `PIPBONG_APP_PROFILE=1` / `PIPBONG_WORKFLOW_PROFILE=1`.

## Output (single file — AI entry point)

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| **`app-profile/latest.md`** | **Only** log file — overwritten on session end + app shutdown (not on preempt) |
| **`app-profile/trace.json`** | Chrome Trace (same flush) |

Repo root (`PIPBONG_REPO_ROOT` override). No `sessions/` archive.

## AI rules

1. Read **`app-profile/latest.md`** — **Auto diagnosis** first.
2. Do **not** ask user for workflow/block settings (in log).
3. Optional: `.\scripts\analyze-app-profile.ps1`
4. User says **분석해줘** → use this file only.

Full handover: [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) §8.14.
